rows.label: qst002311_msg0001
rows.name:
I have devoted my life to spreading the
teachings of the Acedian Holy See.

rows.label: qst002311_msg0002
rows.name:
Much as I would like to share these
wonders with you all...

rows.label: qst002311_msg0003
rows.name:
Right now, I have my hands full
with explaining matters of the soul
to this Nopon fellow.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0101
rows.name:
Young Mololo will soon be a changed
Nopon, you mark my words.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0102
rows.name:
So please, do as he asks and perform
this small favor.

rows.label: qst002302_msg0103
rows.name:
You will not regret this good deed,
I promise you.
